titleStmt.title: The Catalogue of the fellows and other members of the Royal College of Physicians, London printed October 4, 1695 ; with some necessary amendments and advertisements.

notesStmt.note: Includes "A short account of the institution and nature of the College of Physicians, London. Publish'd by themselves, 1688" and "Dr. Badger's Queries to the monopoly and pretended College of Physicians."
Reproduction of original in the Bodleian Library.
